snippet.title: LEGO Horizon Adventures - Announce Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
"http://www.legohorizonadventures.com/
 
 Join machine hunter Aloy as she leads a colorful crew of heroes through the lush wilderness on a quest to save the world and learn the secrets of her past.
 Dive into boundless adventure, customize to your heart’s content, and take on action-packed battles solo or with friends in co-op.
 
 Coming Holiday 2024!
 
 #ps5 #ps5games #lego #horizon #horizonzerodawn #horizonforbiddenwest
